reviews.review: an emotional journey where the meh emoji gets thrown out of his home and meets his love interest jailbreak, who loves him for who he really is, not who he is programmed to be, and they go out on a quest to get him back into the city. This film is a true masterpiece, and Patrick Stewart's "poop emoji" will be more loved than sponge-bob for the rest of time
